locality: Reserve Naturelle de Bemaraha S.E. of Antsalova. Forest on or below Tsingy hills.
Ankarana Reserve, near Campemant des Angles
Bemaraha massif escarpment c. 20 Km W of Marerano on the Manambolo river. Limestone Karst, Tsingy under canopy of Bussia, semi-deciduous forest. Collected with D. DuPuy, J. Andriantiana & B. Carlson
